prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: I finally got my dream car. I have been wanting this my whole life. I have been so happy since i bought it. Friends i never had are now flocking to me because of my car. I never knew buying my dream car would give me so many new friends. The surprising part of the car was it comes with twelve months of SIRIUS/XM radio. Even more surprising is i receive Howard Stern on my radio. Having all access SIRIUS/XM is a pleasant surprise. Finally,all these years of working hard has paid off. All of those overtime hours has given me the car of my life. I love my new dream car. I love all of my new friends too. This has been so exciting. I do not remember the last time i have been this excited. My life is now complete.
